info.name: Apex Receptacle
info.description:
Apex Litter and Recycling Receptacles offer a wealth of design options and match the rest of the Apex family.
  • Body and lid of corrosion-resistant aluminum with a powdercoat finish
  • Insets available in FSC 100% Jatoba hardwood or Stainless Steel in four finish options (FSC License Code: FSC-C004453)
  • Hinged side access doors for easy servicing
  • Single-stream configuration has a 24-gallon liner
  • Split stream configuration has two 18-gallon half liners
  • Optional raincover of powdercoated aluminum
  • Freestanding or surface mount
  • High recycled content; fully recyclable
